name: MANS WORLD 002-A
description:
3D Render

Inspired by by the color-blocking and messaging with in the lyrics and video for Man's World performed by MARINA.

“Man’s World” is the lead single from Marina’s fifth studio album, Ancient Dreams in a Modern Land. This track describes the inequality faced by women and members of the LGBTQ+ community, with reference to climate change and eco-feminism.
